title: Kenmore Apartments...Newly Remodeled One Bedroom Apartment! CALL NOW!
posting_body: ['We will have a gorgeous newly remodeled one bedroom apartment available.', 'This is in the Mid-Wilshire/Koreatown area that is close to many shopping areas, restaurants, schools, markets, etc.', "It is a walker's paradise if you decide to take a stroll without the car.", 'This unit has hardwood floors throughout with linoleum in kitchen which a stove in the kitchen.', 'Plenty of closet space with air conditioner and heater.', 'Parking is included with the rent, as well as laundry facility in the building.', 'Close to the Red Line.', 'Call today and make an appointment to see the unit!', 'Pictures in this ad are a representation and may not reflect the actual apartment that is currently available.', 'To View a virtual tour of unit 14 - 1Bed/1Bath - <URL>', '-Quoted security deposit is on approved credit .', '-6 or 12 month lease - Six month lease available with $200 surcharge .', 'The rent, deposit, concession and terms listed in this ad are only valid for the actual date that this ad was initially posted.']
